Tarea TAS11 - vistas
INVOICE-VIEW
Visualizar la tabla vista antes de crear

    Sentencia:

SELECT i.id, i.code, i.created_at, i.total, c.fullname
FROM invoice i 
JOIN client c 
ON c.id= i.client_id;

    Captura:
TAS10/capturas/1v.png


Guardar la vista de factura para buscarlo solo con select

    Sentencia:

CREATE VIEW invoice_view AS
SELECT i.id, i.code, i.created_at, i.total, c.fullname
FROM invoice i 
JOIN client c 

    Captura:

![alt text](2v.png)
Buscar con Seleccionar el factura.view

    Sentencia:

SELECT * FROM invoice_view;

    Captura:

![alt text](3v.png)
DETAIL.VIEW
Visualizar el view de detail para buscarlo solo con seleccion

    Sentencia:

SELECT d.id, d.quantity, p.description, d.price, d.quantity * p.price AS subtotal
FROM detail d JOIN product p
ON p.id = d.product_id;

    Captura:

![alt text](4v.png)
Guardar el view de detalle para buscarlo solo con seleccion

    Sentencia:

CREATE VIEW detail_view AS
SELECT d.id, d.quantity, p.description, d.price, d.quantity * p.price AS subtotal
FROM detail d JOIN product p
ON p.id = d.product_id;

    Captura:

![alt text](5v.png)
Buscar con Seleccionar el detalle.view

    Sentencia:

SELECT * FROM detail_view;

    Captura:

![alt text](6v.png)
